      "span_text": "These included: (a) children's willingness to engage in conversation with the friend and the 'connectedness' of their dialogue (i.e. the extent to which conversation continued on a shared theme between children;  , (b) the extent of conflict (arguing and tussling over toy) and (c) the extent to which children worked together (i.e. cooperated) with the friend on the drawing task."
